# Definition of Done (Mini)

For any substantial feature/fix/refactor, completion requires:

- code implementation is complete and coherent
- tests are added/updated for changed behavior
- docs are updated (`README.md` and/or `docs/*`) when behavior/workflow changed
- changelog updated under `## [Unreleased]`
- quality checks pass:
  - `pnpm run lint`
  - `pnpm run tsc`
  - `pnpm run test`
  - `pnpm run build`

## Final handoff should include

- what changed
- validation commands run and outcomes
- known limitations or follow-ups
- rollback/risk note for impactful changes
